				\begin{document}$$\:-$$\end{document}” indicates a negative effect (OR < 1) specific to each bird species regarding the outbreaks. In such instances, the possibility of outbreaks within the area of that land-cover type is considerably low. Detailed estimates of individual species are provided in Appendix 2.

